                    <p>HTML Ordered List or Numbered List displays elements in numbered format. The HTML ol tag is used for ordered list. We can use ordered list to represent items either in numerical order format or alphabetical order format, or any format whwre an order is emphasized. There can be different types of numbered list:</p><br>
